=head1 NAME

SimpleLinks - collection of links


=head1 INSTALLATION

To install this application,
first, install module L<Module::Install>
by the following command:

    cpan Module::Install

next, to make Makefile, build this application and run tests
by the following command:

    cpan -t .

finally, to deploy this application
by the following command:

    make install


=head1 DEPENDENCIES

See C<Makefile.PL>.


=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is Perl sample application,
with Ark framework and Data::Model object/data mapper.

See further document of this application by the following commands:

    perldoc SimpleLinks


